Announcement








Solution





With proven track records and vast experience in various industries, our expertise and know-how enable us to provide strategic direction and consultancy to our client on how best to tailor, implement and manage a loyalty program effectively to meet the intended objectives.

						From establishing cost-benefit study to defining project framework and structure, from corporate branding to communication strategies, from implementation to management and maintenance of marketing activities, we will guide our clients through. At a more in-depth level, we provide marketing insights based on the study of customer profile and their behavioral trend and tailor targeted personalized marketing activities.

						Our expertise goes beyond developing a program from scratch as we also provide strategic consulting to overhaul and spice up any existing programs for better efficiency.

						From strategic consultancy, action plans are to be carried out through our 5 Total Integrated Service Components.








Business Intelligence


Contact Center Management


Integrated Marketing Services


Technology Infrastructure


Procurement and Fulfillment









Crystalising the strategic thinking requires reliable facts and figures that give insights. A critical component in Customer Loyalty Management, our Business Intelligence services uses a multi channel data warehousing tool to assist our clients in gaining better insights about their customer and behaviour. Using these analytics, it makes planning for customized marketing activities and products possible. Hence, this would inevitably contribute towards building a life long relationship with the customers.









Equipped with sophisticated technology and system that completes with auto calls distribution and phone recording, our Contact Centre is highly integrated to the data warehouse and fulfillment system. With more than 100 seaters capacity, the contact centre has well-trained professional agents that are able to provide Inbound and Outbound Contact Management. From Customer Service Management to Telesales Management, Relationship Management to Contest Management, we can tailor a contact centre solution for our client's needs.









We provide outsourced integrated marketing services that help our clients build a sustainable corporate brand within the loyalty program to maintain a close relationship with their key customers. Our approach is to create a focused strategy, develop clear value propositions and deliver targeted relationship marketing activities that enhance the program effectiveness. We have helped clients to strategise and conceptualise various marketing programs that include Integrated Marketing Management, Events Management, Special Project Management and Home Shopping Management. Whatever your business needs, budgets and business requirements, we could tailor an integrated marketing solution for you.









We offers consultancy and services that assist our clients to maximized efficiency by integrating our one-stop integrated loyalty management value chain to their in-house infrastructure. In addition, with heavy investment made in acquiring secured servers, data warehousing servers and other advanced technology equipments, our clients can just ride on our technology infrastructure easily.









As we are supporting many loyalty programs in the country as well as in the region, we consolidate worldwide merchandise procurement so as to transfer the best price and the widest product varieties to our clients. Best of all, we provide a one-stop warehousing and fulfilment hub that effectively manage both the inventory and smooth distribution of rewards to our customers.













