                                                Advance Information Marketing Bhd
                                             Company Snapshot
                                            









                                            
	Advance Information Marketing Bhd operates in the Management consulting services sector.
	
	In addition to historical fundamental analyses, the complete report available to purchase compares Advance Information Marketing Bhd with three other
	miscellaneous service companies in Asia:
		
	Tri Viet Asset Management Corporation JSC
	
		of Vietnam
		(2016
	sales of 43.22 billion Dong [US$1.90  million]
		),
	
	Imperium Crown Ltd
	
		of Singapore
		(4.74 million Singapore Dollars [US$3.50  million]
		), and
	
	Axcelasia Inc
	
		(16.18 million Malaysian Ringgits [US$3.78  million]
		).
	
	Sales Analysis. 
	Advance Information Marketing Bhd reported sales of 12.29 million Malaysian Ringgits (US$2.87 million)
		for the
		
		year ending
		December of 2016.
	
		This
		
			represents
		
			a
			
				sharp
			
			decrease of 41.7%
		
		 versus 2015, when the company's sales were 21.06 million Malaysian Ringgits.
	

	




 


 
 


 
 


 
 











 



 













 










